                    "trigger": "You are targeted by a spell",
                    "effect": "The ring replicates the effects of an 8th-level  *spell turning* with a counteract modifier of +35, possibly causing the triggering spell to reflect back on its caster. The ring can reflect no more than 9 total levels of spells per day. If you activate the ring to reflect a spell that would exceed this limit, the attempt fails, but the attempted usage of the ring does not count toward the daily limit.",
